<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.4/css/bootstrap.min.css">

    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.3/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/jquery.ui.widget.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/jquery.iframe-transport.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/jquery.fileupload.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/jquery.cloudinary.js"></script>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.4/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css">
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.4/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Yeseva+One' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
  </head>

  <body>

    <!-- navigation panel -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-default navbar-fixed-top" role="navigation" id="test">
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <!-- Brand and toggle get grouped for better mobile display -->
        <div class="navbar-header">
          <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbar-collapse-main">
            <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbar-collapse-main">
          <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
            <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#startfinding">Start Finding</a></li>
            <li><a href="#howitworks">How it Works</a></li>
            <li><a href="#information">About the Developer</a></li>

          </ul>
        </div><!-- /.navbar-collapse -->
      </div><!-- /.container-fluid -->
    </nav>

    <!-- first section - Home -->
    <div id="home" class="home">
      <div class="text-vcenter">
        <h1> <%= title %> </h1>
        <a href="#startfinding" class="btn btn-default btn-lg">Continue</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- /first section -->

    <!-- second section - About -->
    <div id="startfinding" class="pad-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <p id="findme">
              find Me
            </p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary col-md-5" href="../photo_upload">Start Finding</a>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6 text-center">
            <h2>So many images, so little time.</h2>
            <p class="lead">Let me do the heavy lifting. Upload a collection of images, show me who you are looking for and I'll give you a set of images with that person in them.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- /second section -->

    <!-- third section - How it Works -->
    <div id="howitworks" class="pad-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center">How it Works</h2> <hr />
        <div class="row text-center">
          <div class="col-sm-3 col-xs-6">
            <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-camera"> </i>
            <h4>Step 1</h4>
            <p>Click the <a href="../photo_upload" id="incognito_link">Start Finding</a> button above. Then upload a collection of images by simply dragging the images to the image window.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-3 col-xs-6">
            <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-record"> </i>
            <h4>Step 2</h4>
            <p>Select a target image. It should be a photograph of just the person you want to find. Front facing photos are best.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-3 col-xs-6">
            <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-search"> </i>
            <h4>Step 3</h4>
            <p>I will search the collection of images that you uploaded and compare each face in each image to the target image.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-3 col-xs-6">
            <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok"> </i>
            <h4>Step 4</h4>
            <p>Take a look at the results and enjoy the time savings.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- /third section -->

    <!-- fourth section - Information -->
    <div id="information" class="pad-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <div class="panel panel-default">
              <div class="panel-heading">
                <h2 class="panel-title">About Teddi</h2>
              </div>
              <div class="panel-body lead">

              <p>
                I am a full stack web developer and I build apps for the web using Ruby on Rails and Node with Express.

              </p>

              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <div class="panel panel-default">
              <div class="panel-heading">
                <h2 class="panel-title">More projects by Teddi</h2>
              </div>
              <div class="panel-body lead">
                To see more information about other projects I have worked on, check out my portfolio. Some projects I've created are:
                <li>Clean Kids Chore Chart Generator</li>
                <li>gCamp, a Project Management App</li>
                <li>a Round Robin Tournament Creation App</li>
                <li>a U.S. Farmer's Market API</li>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- /fourth section -->

    <!-- fifth section -->
    <div id="howitworks" class="pad-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-12 text-center">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- footer -->
    <footer>
      <hr />
      <div class="container">
        <p class="text-right">Project Developed by <a href="http://teddicodes.wordpress.com/">Teddi Maull</a></p>
        <p class="text-right">
          Image Credits:
          computer image is from <a href="https://unsplash.com/galymzhanabdugalimov">Galymzhan Abdugalimov</a>,
          library image is from <a href="http://www.unsplash.com/p">Patrik GÃ¶the</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </footer>
    <!-- /footer -->


  </body>
</html>
